summary: do your favorite show for the asks
question: do your favorite show for the asks
answer:
-Game of Thrones-

My favorite Episode: OMG its the part where Jon, Tormund, Gendry and the other guys fight the Walkers with Dany!

My least Favorite Episode: anytime Ramsay Bolton was onscreen.

My favorite Arc: Sansa Stark going from “I want to be a princess” to being the badass Queen of the North we know she truly is.

My lease favorite Arc: anything involving Jaime and Cersei

My favorite ship: Sansa x Gendry, the Hound & Arya’s BROTP, Jon x Ygritte … and more

My favorite character: Brienne, Pod, Tyrion, GENDRY

My favorite season: alllll of them

My least favorite: the season with the Red Wedding

Who I wish would have stayed till the end: Shireen 😩

Who I wish would have left the show sooner: Ramsay lol

Who I think is the most cheated character: Arya in a way

Who got more screen time than they maybe should: Dany

What drew me to it: I’d read the books

What kept me watching: drama, sex and blood

If I would recommend it: hell yes!!

summary: I have been sold like a broodmare. I've been chained and betrayed, raped and defiled. Do you know what kept me standing, through...
body:
I have been sold like a broodmare. I’ve been chained and betrayed, raped and defiled. Do you know what kept me standing, through all those years in exile? Faith. Not in any god, not in myths and legends. In myself.

Daenerys Targaryen.
